# Senior Site Reliability Engineer (SRE) – Skills & Lab Guide

## Overview

This repository is a comprehensive reference for **Senior SREs**, covering:

- Systems & Linux
- Networking
- Git & Version Control
- Bash & Python scripting
- Databases (RDBMS & NoSQL)
- AWS Cloud & IaC
- CI/CD pipelines
- Observability & Monitoring
- Incident Management

It is designed for **hands-on labs** and **automation-focused learning** for top-tier SRE roles.

---

## Core Responsibilities

- Design, operate, and maintain **highly available systems**
- Automate repetitive tasks and CI/CD pipelines
- Monitor, alert, and troubleshoot incidents
- Manage **cloud infrastructure & databases**
- Implement security best practices
- Create **runbooks and postmortems**
- Mentor junior engineers

